title: Code Breakers Book Bundle

description: What do you get when you mix a death lottery, lethal artificial intelligence and three hackers? The making of an incredible and thrilling book series called Code Breakers. A dismal future forces human survivors into the confines of a domed city that’s controlled by an umbral organization. To save the lives of those within, as well as his own, one man must flee to the wastelands beyond. Discover what awaits and download the Code Breaker book bundle today. Be forewarned. Code Breakers is an addicting and titillating ride that you won’t want to end. Make sure to click the ‘get more books’ button to find out how it ends. Visit  Colin F. Barnes's website   to find out more about the series. Source:   http://www.vuze.com/featured-content/colin-barnes-code-breakers-book-bundle/
